about.summary: SAT solver for use in Enstaller, based on the MiniSat implementation

name: simplesat
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "simplesat" %}
{% set version = "0.8.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: afc4a266d1875666a206424982846ae1f3db6c57e91088e94964fb440179179e

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - attrs >=16.1.0
    - okonomiyaki >=0.16.6
    - six >=1.10.0
    - enum34  # [py27]

test:
  imports:
    - simplesat

about:
  home: https://github.com/enthought/sat-solver
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'SAT solver for use in Enstaller, based on the MiniSat implementation'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - hmaarrfk
